{
  "title": "Tunisian Soy-Glazed Tagine",
  "description": "A pungent and savory Tunisian date-night dish featuring soy sauce and lacquer-glaze, perfect for lacto-vegetarians. This rich and aromatic tagine is best served over couscous.",
